<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1436,1051,1221]" pageId="14" pageNumber="574">
[
<emphasis bold="true" box="[161,341,1051,1077]" pageId="14" pageNumber="574">Author’s Note:</emphasis>
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3015251319" collectionCode="CNC, USNM" country="United States of America" county="Cotypes" location="There" municipality="Hull" pageId="14" pageNumber="574" specimenCount="58" specimenCount-female="13" specimenCount-male="16" typeStatus="holotype">
According to Ms Lisa Bartels (
<collectionCode box="[705,768,1051,1077]" country="Canada" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/y2kv-9w3k" name="Canadian National Collection of Insects, Arachnids, and Nematodes" pageId="14" pageNumber="574">CNC</collectionCode>
), there are 
<specimenCount box="[896,1031,1051,1078]" pageId="14" pageNumber="574" type="generic" typeStatus="syntypes">29 syntypes</specimenCount>
housed in the Hull collection; Hull stated at the end of the published description that there were 
<specimenCount box="[824,913,1087,1113]" pageId="14" pageNumber="574" type="male">16 male</specimenCount>
and 
<specimenCount box="[966,1077,1087,1113]" pageId="14" pageNumber="574" type="female">13 female</specimenCount>
cotypes, in addition to the 
<typeStatus pageId="14" pageNumber="574">holotype</typeStatus>
and 
<typeStatus box="[255,348,1123,1149]" pageId="14" pageNumber="574">allotype</typeStatus>
, suggesting the subsequent destruction of two specimens. 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:2845F361FFF8F664D5F4FC2186D2479D:A53314ACFFF8F664D688FB9183364725" box="[1003,1068,1123,1149]" country="United States of America" county="Cotypes" municipality="Hull" name="There" pageId="14" pageNumber="574">There</location>
are no specimens in the 
<collectionCode box="[1348,1432,1123,1149]" country="USA" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34871" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34871" name="Smithsonian Institution, National Museum of Natural History" pageId="14" pageNumber="574" type="Museum">USNM</collectionCode>
, (
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:2845F361FFF8F664D5F4FC2186D2479D:A53314ACFFF8F664D5FCFB75864747F9" box="[159,349,1159,1185]" country="United States of America" county="Cotypes" municipality="Hull" name="Chris Thompson" pageId="14" pageNumber="574">Chris Thompson</location>
, pers. comm.) despite the fact that 
<collectingMunicipality box="[731,781,1159,1185]" pageId="14" pageNumber="574">Hull</collectingMunicipality>
clearly stated that “ 
<collectingCounty box="[997,1092,1159,1185]" pageId="14" pageNumber="574">Cotypes</collectingCounty>
will be deposited in the 
<collectingCountry name="United States of America" pageId="14" pageNumber="574">United States</collectingCountry>
National Museum.”]
</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
